description: The iShares Paris-Aligned Climate Optimized MSCI USA ETF seeks to track the investment results of an index composed of U.S. large-and mid-capitalization stocks that is designed to be compatible with the objectives of the Paris Agreement by, in aggregate, following a decarbonization trajectory, reducing exposure to climate-related transition and physical risks and increasing exposure to companies favorably positioned for the transition to a low-carbon economy.
name: iShares Paris-Aligned Climate Optimized MSCI USA ETF
